13:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Sonni yozuvga o'giruvchi raqamli summalarni o'zbek va rus tillarida matnli ko'rinishga aylantiradi. Bu vosita O'zbekistondagi buxgalterlar, yuristlar va tadbirkorlarga shartnomalar, hisob-fakturalar, ishonchnomalar, bajarilgan ishlar dalolatnomalari va to'lov topshiriqnomalarini to'ldirishda zarur — bu hujjatlarda summa yozuv bilan ko'rsatilishi shart."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda buxgalteriya hisobi talablariga ko'ra, birlamchi hujjatlarda summa raqamlar bilan yoziladi va yozuv bilan takrorlanadi. Summa yozuvidagi xatolik hujjatning bank yoki soliq inspektsiyasi tomonidan rad etilishiga olib kelishi mumkin. Konverter bunday xatolarni bartaraf etib, son turlanishi qoidalarini hisobga olgan holda to'g'ri yozuvni avtomatik shakllantiradi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Vosita 0 dan trilliongacha summalarni qo'llab-quvvatlaydi va uchta valyuta bilan ishlaydi: o'zbek so'mi (so'm/tiyin), AQSh dollari (dollar/sent) va yevro. Misol: 15 750 000 → «o'n besh million yetti yuz ellik ming so'm 00 tiyin». Rus tilida ham to'g'ri shakl hosil bo'ladi: «пятнадцать миллионов семьсот пятьдесят тысяч сум 00 тийин»."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Amaliy foydalanish holatlari: ish haqi ko'rsatilgan mehnat shartnomasini rasmiylashtirish, kontragent uchun to'lov hisob-fakturasini tayyorlash, tovar-moddiy boyliklarni olish uchun ishonchnoma to'ldirish, pul mablag'larini olish haqida tilxat tuzish. Bu holatlarning barchasida konverter vaqtni tejaydi va grammatik aniqlikni kafolatlaydi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Konverter rus va o'zbek tillarining xususiyatlarini to'g'ri qayta ishlaydi: rus tilida — jins bo'yicha turlanish (одна тысяча, два миллиона, пять тысяч), o'zbek tilida — qo'shma sonlarning to'g'ri yozilishi. Raqamni kiriting — natijani nusxalab istalgan hujjatga qo'yish mumkin. Vosita bir lahzada ishlaydi va sahifa yuklangandan keyin internet ulanishini talab qilmaydi."}]]}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Ko'p beriladigan savollar"}],["$","$L18",null,{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card px-4","children":[["$","$L19","0",{"value":"faq-0","children":[["$","$L1a",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"Sonni yozuvga o'giruvchi nima uchun kerak?"}],["$","$L1b",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"Summa yozuv bilan ko'rsatilishi kerak bo'lgan moliyaviy hujjatlarni to'ldirish uchun."}]}]]}],"$L1c","$L1d"]}]]}],"$L1e"]}]
